</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Birkhoff–von_Neumann_decomposition"><span id="Birkhoff.E2.80.93von_Neumann_decomposition"></span>Birkhoff–von Neumann decomposition</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Magic_square&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Birkhoff–von Neumann decomposition"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
