<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Multiplicative_magic_squares_of_complex_numbers">Multiplicative magic squares of complex numbers</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Magic_square&amp;action=edit&amp;section=33" title="Edit section: Multiplicative magic squares of complex numbers"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
